Ask HN: Who is maintaining Aaron Swartz's website?
text:
I just learned that the RSS feed on Paul Graham's blog is generated by, and hosted at, aaronsw.com [1, 2]. Who is maintaining this code and domain?

I'd be impressed if the scraper still remains unmodified after all these years.

[1] http://www.paulgraham.com/rss.html [2] http://www.aaronsw.com/2002/feeds/pgessays.rss

title: Ask HN: Is There a Directory of Towns Paying for Immigrants?
text:
I've read articles about old towns in Italy and Japan paying people lots of money to move into an old house, fix it up, and stay for a while.

Is there a website that offers a directory of these programs all around the world? It sounds like something I'd really like to do in maybe 5 years.
